  <scopecontent audience="internal" id="aspace_77817ff4023f231373741135d759e14e">
    <head>Scope and content</head>
<p>37 painted fabric banners featuring 32 different sign designs, produced by the Ithaca Sign Company for various stores, businesses, fairs, and political campaigns in cities such as Springfield; Utica, N. Y.; Manchester; Poughkeepsie, N. Y.; Syracuse, N. Y.; Rockville, Md; Millville; Altamont, N. Y.; Trenton; Muskogee; Ogden; New York City, N. Y.; Dallas, Texas; and Los Angeles, Calif.</p>  </scopecontent>
